name: PHOTO - "Which SIDE of the GLASS?"
description:
Photograph by HP LoveBux 
Salem, MA. October 2021


This is a shop-window display with reflections.
No filters or enhancements were done

This is the image, just as it came through the lens.

I will be using this as the basis for a painting later ...
So I'm minting 25 of the source photo as a freebie promo = .025 Tez 
Once the FULL collection of paintings is released, 
any remain tokens for this original 
source photo edition will be burned. 


The COLLECTION will be called 'Witch City"
Images from SALEM MA taken in October 2021.

Grab this now and enjoy. 

HP LoveBux
